  ('judicial-f0899a01-moex-00165', 'judicial-f0899a01', 'judicial-f0899a01-moex-113-0f9358e7', 'sub-judicial-f0899a01-03', NULL, 'essay', '監察院以甲違反法官法第 18 條第 1 項及法官倫理規範第 3 條等規定，
